{"search_data": "RajasthanLadli Laxmi Yojana to be Implemented in RajasthanWhat is Ladli Laxmi YojanaUnder Ladli Laxmi Yojana, the state government purchases National Savings Certificate of Rs 6,000 each year for five years and these would be renewed from time to time. The certificates are purchased in the name of a girl every year after her birth. The beneficiary girl is given some amount upon admission in different standards as mentioned below:\u2013 INR 2000 at the time of girl\u2019s admission in the sixth standard \u2013 INR 4000 at the time of admission in ninth standard \u2013 INR 7500 when she gets admitted in the 11th standardDuring higher secondary education of the girl, she would get Rs 200 every month.And, on completion of 21 years, the remaining amount which would be more than Rs 1 lakh is given to the girl.IMG CREDIT: http://web1163.165.new.ocpwebserver.com  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}